- Tests-first:
  - RED->GREEN->REFACTOR; deterministic seeds; failure-path tests mandatory
  - Unit, integration, property-based where applicable

- Benchmarks:
  - Micro-bench hot paths (context retrieval, scheduling)
  - Regressions <= 5% for key metrics; document SLOs and environment



